Recommends: avahi-daemon
Description: Software KVM switch for sharing keyboard and mouse
 Konflikt is a software KVM switch that allows you to share a single
 keyboard and mouse across multiple computers. It supports seamless
 mouse movement between screens, clipboard synchronization, and
 automatic server discovery via mDNS (Avahi/Bonjour).
 .
 Features:
  - Seamless mouse and keyboard sharing
  - Clipboard synchronization (text)
  - Automatic server discovery (mDNS)
  - Configurable screen edge transitions
  - Hotkey for cursor lock toggle
